OL,3,CMotorcyclist Aran Sadler dies in race
OL,4,Cat Scarborough's Oliver's Mount
OL,6,FCounty Durham racer Aran Sadler has
OL,7,Fdied at an event in Scarborough.
OL,9,FAround 3.20pm on Saturday 11 April,
OL,10,FAran Sadler came off a Kawasaki ZX636
OL,11,Fduring a race at Oliver's Mount in
OL,12,FScarborough. He died at the scene.
OL,14,FRace organisers said: "It is with
OL,15,Fprofound sadness that we announce the
OL,16,Fpassing of Aran Sadler, following an
OL,17,Fincident in SuperSport A Race 1 at
OL,18,Ftoday's Spring Cup.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
