OL,3,CMotorcyclist Aran Sadler dies in race
OL,4,Cat Scarborough's Oliver's Mount
OL,6,F"Aran was a tremendously popular
OL,7,Fmember of our paddock community and a
OL,8,Fchampion several times over at
OL,9,FOliver's Mount. He will be deeply
OL,10,Fmissed by everyone who knew him and
OL,11,Fraced alongside him.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts are entirely with Aran's
OL,14,Ffamily and his partner Lorna at this
OL,15,Fdevastating time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
