OL,3,CMotorcyclist Aran Sadler dies in race
OL,4,Cat Scarborough's Oliver's Mount
OL,6,F"After consulting with Aran's family,
OL,7,Fracing will continue tomorrow. We ask
OL,8,Feveryone ` in the paddock and in the
OL,9,Fgrandstands ` to keep Aran in their
OL,10,Fthoughts and to continue the
OL,11,Fconsideration shown to Aran's family
OL,12,Fand friends as it has been today.
OL,14,F"We are grateful to everyone who
OL,15,Fshowed patience and respect in waiting
OL,16,Ffor this official statement to be
OL,17,Freleased. It means a great deal to
OL,18,FAran's family and to us."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
