OL,3,CMotorcyclist Aran Sadler dies in race
OL,4,Cat Scarborough's Oliver's Mount
OL,6,FTeesside Motorsports paid tribute: "We
OL,7,Fare extremely saddened to hear of the
OL,8,Fpassing of Aran Sadler following an
OL,9,Fincident at Oliver's Mount.
OL,11,F"Aran was a familiar and valued face
OL,12,Fat Teesside, attending many events
OL,13,Fover the years, and he will be greatly
OL,14,Fmissed by all who knew him.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts and condolences are with
OL,17,Fhis family, friends, and the wider
OL,18,Fracing community at this difficult
OL,19,Ftime. Rest in peace, Aran."
